Installation

1. Install Allegro 5
Allegro 5.0.0rc3 or later from http://alleg.sourceforge.net/
If this issue is not fixed <https://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=detail&aid=3143062&group_id=5665&atid=105665>, then:
  patch -p0 < allegro-osx-argv0.patch
Install per directions in README

2. Compile Leggo my Allegro
make
make leggo

3. Run sample
./leggo
